Title: Cox's Blocks, a Minecraft server from Do By Friday
Description: You can join the server by typing "coxblocks.rocks" in the Multiplayer menu of your Minecraft: Java Edition client. You can use the "Direct Connect" option, but we recommend using "Add Server" to permanently add the server to your server bookmarks list. The server is running Java 1.15.2.

Many applications can be launched using a URI. Of course, you can start your favorite web browser using an URL such as https://www.meziantou.net. But you can also start you mail app using mailto:email@sample.com, or skype using skype:pseudo.
